<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material" key="marmor">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType" reg="Architrave block">cornice block</rs> still partly buried (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.71</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.20</measure> visible x <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.66</measure> visible), with <rs type="decoration">beading</rs> above and below the inscribed fascia.</p></div><div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of Text</head><p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on one fascia. The text must have begun on a preceding, and continued on a subsequent block.</p>
</div><div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of Letters</head><p>av. <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.035</measure>, not entirely even in height; triangular stop after the name.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
Perhaps <date cert="low" exact="none" notAfter="0200" notBefore="0067">late first to second centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)
[[but ask about beading]]</p>
</div>
